<hymn_number>5276</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lạis̊mika ạl̊qudũwsi nuh̊dī
 kulã sẖuk̊riⁿ yā karīm̊
 biạkẖ̊tīāriⁿ jī̊̉ta taf̊dī
 jin̊sanā ạl̊ʿāṣī ạlạảtẖīm̊

[V2]
 2- qābilạaⁿ maẘta ạlṣãlībi
 sẖāribaⁿạ kā̊̉sa ạl̊gẖaḍab̊
 min̊ yadi ạl̊ʿad̊li ạlrãhībi
 ại̹nã hadẖā laʿajab̊

[V3]
 3- fī yadi ạlậbi wadaʿ̊ta
 ạlrũwḥa wālậbu ạs̊tajāb̊
 muẓ̊hiraⁿạ kulã ạlrĩḍā ại̹dẖ̊
 sẖaqã dẖalika ạl̊ḥijāb̊

[V4]
 4- falidẖā biạl̊qal̊bi nub̊dī
 laka ḥam̊daⁿạ mus̊tadīm̊
 lạis̊mika ạl̊qudũwsi nuh̊dī
 kulã sẖuk̊riⁿ yā karīm̊</lyrics>
<title>lạsmk ạlqdws nhdy</title>
</song>